chunk_content: This indicator is harmonized with GAM indicator “Percentage of pregnant women living with HIV who received antiretroviral medicine to reduce the risk of MTCT of HIV.” How to collect: For the numerator: the source of this information is national program records aggregated from program monitoring tools, such as patient registers and summary reporting forms. The numerator can be generated by counting the number of pregnant women living with HIV who received antiretrovirals to reduce MTCT in the reporting period, by regimen.
